Invocation Name: who am i
des:
Start your day with a reminder of who you are and what you can accomplish. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
A lot of people are battling depression, anxiety, insecurity, and low self-esteem in their daily living. This unhealthy mental state inhibits productivity and sometimes it leads to suicidal tendencies. This skill was created to help users overcome a lack of self-confidence/depression and improve mental/emotional health by reminding users of their true identity and capabilities.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
